ime Day 促销期间找到最优惠的价格&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /21502865/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得的最佳 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div >; &lt;p id=&quot;1dZhWj&quot;>;下面，我们精选了一些我们可以亲自担保的低于 50 美元的商品。当然，它们包括许多亚马逊自己的设备，包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，最新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Spot-TP-Link -Smart-Color/dp/B0DF15V76B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Spot&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com /Amazon-smart-plug-works-with-Alexa/dp/B089DR29T6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊便宜的智能插头&lt;/a>;。非亚马逊上也有很多值得注意的交易...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech- Deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T11:50:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T11:50:09-04:00</updated><title> Prime Day AirPods Pro 2 价格比以往任何时候都低至 169 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;AirPods Pro 2022 型号坐在橙色底座上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6L9e1JNbxhIi7jOJUqsNRPl7jyA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639692/226285_AIRPODS_PRO_2_cwelch_ 0011.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;