uit-state-attorneys-general-kids-mental-health" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265169/tiktok-lawsuit-state-attorneys-general-kids-mental-health</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-08T11:17:23-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-08T11:17:23-04:00</updated><title>兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research) 指控 Roblox 在用户数量上向投资者撒谎</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Roblox 的屏幕截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MZVZ0uoDbTZRMKf3BzWyYpHAoH0=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/73639644/roblox_screenshot.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Roblox&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3k5r5n&quot;>;Roblox 面临指控，称其向投资者谎报了参与该项目的人数使用该平台。在周二发布的一份报告中，&lt;a href=&quot;https://hindenburgresearch.com/roblox/&quot;>;投资公司 Hindenburg Research&lt;/a>; 声称 Roblox“始终将其平台上的人数夸大了 25%， 42% 或更多。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;edwRHg&quot;>;Roblox，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/11/19/21578491/roblox-ipo-announced-dau -increase-pandemic&quot;>;于 2021 年上市&lt;/a>;，据报道 &lt;a href=&quot;https://ir.roblox.com/news/news-details/2024/Roblox-Reports-Second-Quarter-2024- Financial-Results/default.aspx#:~:text=non%2DGAAP%20guidance.-,基于%20on%20the%20carrying%20amount%20of%20deferred%20revenue%20and%20deferred,2024%20and%20an%20increase%20in ”在最近的收益报告中，每日活跃用户数为 7950 万&lt;/a>;。然而，Hindenburg 声称 Roblox “故意将”真实用户与日常用户混为一谈，因为该数字还可能包括替代帐户和机器人。研究称，Roblox 可以将替代帐户与单个用户分开，尽管该公司披露称每日活跃用户“并不是衡量独特个人的标准......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265145/roblox-hindenburg-reseach-dau-child-safety-short-seller-report&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265145/roblox-hindenburg-reseach-dau-child-safety-short-seller-report" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265145/roblox-hindenburg-reseach-dau-child-safety-short-seller-report</id><auth